DM Chatbot ‚Äì Setup Guide (READ FIRST)



This workflow is an Instagram DM chatbot built using n8n.
Before importing and running the JSON file, you must complete the setup below.

If any step is skipped, the workflow will not function correctly.

What This Workflow Does

Listens for incoming Instagram DMs

Sends the message content to an AI agent

Automatically replies to the user via Instagram Graph API

This workflow does NOT send cold DMs and does NOT scrape users.



Requirements (Mandatory)
1. n8n Account

You must have an active n8n account:

n8n Cloud or

Self-hosted n8n instance

Create one here:
https://n8n.io



2. Instagram Business Account

Must be an Instagram Business or Creator account

Must be connected to a Facebook Page

Instagram messaging via Meta must be enabled

‚ö†Ô∏è Personal Instagram accounts will not work.



3. Meta (Facebook) App Configuration

You need a Meta App with:

Instagram Graph API enabled

Webhooks enabled

Required permissions:

instagram_manage_messages

pages_manage_metadata

pages_read_engagement

You must have:

Instagram Page ID

Instagram User ID

Long-lived Access Token



4. Webhook Setup

Inside your Meta App:

Add a Webhook subscription for Instagram

Use the Webhook URL generated by n8n

Verification token must be exactly:

testn8n



5. OpenRouter API Key (AI Replies)

This workflow uses OpenRouter for AI responses.

Steps:

Create an account at https://openrouter.ai

Generate an API key

Add it inside n8n as a credential:

Credential type: OpenRouter

Paste your API key

After Importing the JSON (Required Edits)



1. HTTP Request Node

Replace the placeholder token with your own Instagram access token:

Bearer YOUR_INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN


Never use someone else‚Äôs token.



2. AI System Prompt (Optional but Recommended)

Edit the system prompt to match your brand tone and use case.

How to Run the Workflow

Import the JSON file into n8n

Configure all required credentials

Activate the workflow

Send a DM to your Instagram account

The chatbot replies automatically

Important Notes

This workflow only responds to incoming messages

No scraping

No cold outreach

Instagram rate limits still apply

This is not plug-and-play without setup

